	(26,2,'2014-08-20 03:39:31','2014-08-20 03:39:31','Don’t Even Tripp Production is in the process of setting up its Board of Trustees. Are you not only an avid fan but supporter of theatre and are looking to contribute to Don’t Even Tripp’s ongoing success? Contact us at donteventripp@gmail.com for more information how to join our exciting new board!\r\n\r\nUpcoming Projects:\r\n\r\nOur next original production, \"Generation of Dreams\" coming to you Spring 2015! Be on the lookout for specific dates, locations and ticket information. As well as our production blog so you can hear about the step by step process of what goes down behind the scenes with Don\'t Even Tripp.','Updates','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2014-08-20 03:39:31','2014-08-20 03:39:31','',10,'http://donteventripp.com/?p=26',0,'revision','',0),
